All is set to host Mykmary fashion show on August 31, 2019 at Sweet Sensation Banquet Hall, Ikeja Lagos. The show which is hosted by Nollywood actors – Mazi Dr Sam Uche Anyamele and Maureen Okpolo – will shine a spotlight on the city of Lagos introducing Nigeria’s Fashion Industry in partnership with Event News Africa, Spice TV, Connect Nigeria, among others,. It will feature special guests like Moji Oyetayo aka Mama Ajasco, Hakeem Rahman, Mazi Emeka Okoye, Christian Paul, Nigeria Nollywood actor Uncle Tommy Oyewole and others. The organisers said the event promises to represent the best of the Nigerian fashion scene, give exposure to Nigerian fashion designers and create a networking channel between fashion designers and other stakeholders in the fashion industry.